fullerenes as well and complex heavy atoms, such as the lanthanide\natoms. We conclude with a remark on the catalytic properties of the fullerenes\nthrough their negative ions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2017 22:27:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-02"}
