not specific to the studied corpus, but apply to semantic\nchange in general.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2017 10:02:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Mar 2017 15:33:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 30 Nov 2017 21:07:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-04"}
