ean squared distance to the\nfeasible set and, in the case of a compact set, we provide a near-optimal\nsolvability convergence rate of $O\\left(\\frac{k^\\delta\\ln k}{\\sqrt{k}}\\right)$\nin terms of the mean dual gap-function of the SVI for arbitrarily small\n$\\delta>0$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2017 12:50:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Mar 2017 16:52:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-03"}
